-----------------------------------------------------------------
                           Nock.js REPL

This is a fork of https://github.com/famousj/nock.js, but instead
of operating on Node.js, uses a browser-based REPL.

Try it out: just open nock.htm in your browser. If you don't know
what Nock is, try here, http://ow.ly/s80MC, and test out what you
learn in the REPL.


